This is my 3rd surf map *yay*

===

FAQ:

Q: is there a buyzone in this map?
A: yes it's in the secret.

Q: how do i get to the secret?
A: it is behind the middle of spawns.

Q: how do i get out of the secret?
A: in the middle of the room is a button on the ceiling.

Q: why can't i shoot through the fence on jail?
A: cause i hate sniping campers everywhere. only campspot for them is in secret.

Q: why did i get a gun with only 1 clip.
A: you went to fast through the weapon spawner. it spawns bullets if u just walk through it.

===

Perfect for deathmatch.
Map will automatically change airaccelerate to 200 each round.
